ObjectStates.Name: Notecard
ObjectStates.Description:
[b]List of Changes:[/b]
-Fixed All the Broken Models, sadly Stone Crusher Carnifexes Have been Lost to GW's Wrath
-Fixed Heriophant's native Position (it was a bit skwed) and added a new collider to it, hopefully it works better, let me know in the coments (Its on the center bottom of the model)
-Re-Organized all the Unit Types for better searchability

ObjectStates.Name: Notecard
ObjectStates.Description:
An apology for the long absence, its been the usual things like life and school, but i hope i will be a bit more active for now, at this moment i will be working on restoring all my mods, so no much coming in the future, to be fair there is no much missing models
Might Reinstate the Legends models later

ObjectStates.Name: Notecard
ObjectStates.Description:
-Fixed Stats And Names of some models that where wrong, didnt bother adding rule, because Battlescribe2TTS is much better at that and most of you should be using it
-Turned the Tyranocytes Back To generic Models as i had troubles with them when playing them as bags (Bag Tyranocyest are in the bag to the side)

ObjectStates.Name: Notecard
ObjectStates.Description:
A Friendly reminder that i do not own any of the models here i only recolored the skin and changed some, they are all owned by their respective creators, specially the pyrovore made by the fine Vergor because no one else wanted to make it lel
EXCEPT the new Broodlord, but dont worry im not to clingy to stuff, so feel free to use it, modify it or repost it at leisure ;)
